author: Rogue Hobbies
description:
Have you ever walked into a Games Workshop to buy some Warhammer and thought ... If I was in charge, things would be different. 

I think we all have at some point but unfortunately now its time for me to put my money (or lack of it) where my mouth is... 

In this video I play the 'Tabletop Game Shop' Simulator!! A game where you essentially run your own 'Games Workshop' Style tabletop shop! 

And it turns out... im not great at business. 

HOPE YOU ENJOY THE CHAOS ROGUES!
